properties.Name: AminoAcidClass
properties.Description:
The class of the amino acid, which is typically grouped in 6 main classifications.

Ex:
-  Aliphatic
-  Hydroxyl or Sulfur/Selenium-containing
-  Cyclic
-  Aromatic
-  Basic
-  Acidic and their Amide

Columns.Name: AminoAcidClassId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an amino class.

Columns.Name: AminoAcidClassName
Columns.Description: The name of an amino class.

Columns.Name: AminoAcidClassDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an amino class.
